title: The Tale of the Princess Kaguya(2013)(Studio Ghibli)
description: "Found inside a shining stalk of bamboo by an old bamboo cutter and his wife, a tiny girl grows rapidly into an exquisite young lady. The mysterious young princess enthralls all who encounter her - but ultimately she must confront her fate, the punishment for her crime." IMDB source
